<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Speakeasy | Protocol Interrupted</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/terminal.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/auth.css"> </head>
<body>
<div class="auth-wrapper">
    <div class="auth-card" style="border-top-color: #ef4444;">
        <div class="auth-icon">⚠️</div>
        <h1>System Instability</h1>
        <p>The Alchemist’s tools have malfunctioned. The protocol has been safely terminated to prevent reagent contamination.</p>

        <div class="error-msg">
            <%= message %>
        </div>

        <div class="auth-links">
            <a href="/dashboard">Return to the Entrance</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>